<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #00d4ff);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 550px;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: auto;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #007bff;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      p {
        color: #444;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background: #0056b3;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .whatsapp {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #25d366;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }
      .whatsapp:hover {
        background: #1ebe57;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Permintaan Reset Password</h2>
      <p>
        Kami menerima permintaan untuk mengatur ulang password akun AkuCuciin
        Anda.
      </p>
      <p>
        Jika Anda tidak meminta reset password, abaikan email ini. Link reset
        akan kedaluwarsa dalam <strong><%= expirationTime %></strong> menit.
      </p>
      <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
      <p class="footer">
        Jika mengalami masalah, hubungi tim support kami melalui WhatsApp.
      </p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/6285810211200 " class="whatsapp"
        >Hubungi WhatsApp AkuCuciin</a
      >
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
